column5: Was well worth the walk for solitude and steel. First steelie of the day hit a mini pink Riverworm. Hope everyone played nice and had fun. Cheers.
Beauty fish.  I caught the majority of fish on the pink worms also.  I need to stock up before next weekend.
Thanks Tibbs....Jigs were also producing well. Good luck next time out. Cheers
Beauty for sure Great job silverstreak and thanks for sharing Leechman
